column5: Planning on going fishing later .. anyone know who has 2012 licenses available in scarborough?
tried lucky fishing on sheppard aven. east and midland ave. or tried pro fishing on sheppard aven. and warden they have the fishing licence..
I seen the sign at Cedarbrea Canadian Tire.  Jack
You are better off to buy it on line I'm told. The new licence system is a big PITA and took about 15 minutes to sort through at the tackle shops.
